{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# 基因表达数据分析实验\n",
    "\n",
    "本实验将学习如何分析基因表达数据，识别差异表达基因。\n",
    "\n",
    "## 实验目标\n",
    "- 理解基因表达数据的基本结构\n",
    "- 掌握差异表达分析方法\n",
    "- 学会计算Fold Change和p值\n",
    "- 创建火山图和MA图"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "from scipy import stats\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.rcParams['font.sans-serif'] = ['SimHei']\n",
    "plt.rcParams['axes.unicode_minus'] = False\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"库导入成功\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. 加载和探索数据"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "data = {\n",
    "    'Gene': ['Gene1', 'Gene2', 'Gene3', 'Gene4', 'Gene5', \n",
    "            'Gene6', 'Gene7', 'Gene8', 'Gene9', 'Gene10'],\n",
    "    'Control_1': [10.5, 8.2, 12.3, 9.8, 11.2, 10.1, 9.5, 10.8, 11.0, 9.9],\n",
    "    'Control_2': [11.2, 7.9, 12.8, 10.1, 11.5, 10.3, 9.8, 11.0, 11.3, 10.2],\n",
    "    'Treatment_1': [15.3, 14.2, 18.5, 16.1, 17.2, 15.8, 14.9, 16.5, 17.0, 15.5],\n",
    "    'Treatment_2': [16.1, 13.8, 19.2, 15.8, 17.8, 16.2, 15.2, 16.8, 17.5, 15.9]\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
    "df = pd.DataFrame(data)\n",
    "print(\"基因表达数据:\")\n",
    "print(df)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. 计算统计量"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "control_mean = df[['Control_1', 'Control_2']].mean(axis=1)\n",
    "treatment_mean = df[['Treatment_1', 'Treatment_2']].mean(axis=1)\n",
    "\n",
    "df['Control_Mean'] = control_mean\n",
    "df['Treatment_Mean'] = treatment_mean\n",
    "df['Fold_Change'] = treatment_mean / control_mean\n",
    "df['Log2_Fold_Change'] = np.log2(df['Fold_Change'])\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"统计分析:\")\n",
    "print(df[['Gene', 'Control_Mean", "Treatment_Mean", "Fold_Change", "Log2_Fold_Change"]])"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. 差异表达分析"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "control_std = df[['Control_1', 'Control_2']].std(axis=1)\n",
    "treatment_std = df[['Treatment_1', 'Treatment_2']].std(axis=1)\n",
    "\n",
    "n1 = 2\n",
    "n2 = 2\n",
    "\n",
    "pooled_std = np.sqrt(((n1-1)*control_std**2 + (n2-1)*treatment_std**2) / (n1+n2-2))\n",
    "se = pooled_std * np.sqrt(1/n1 + 1/n2)\n",
    "\n",
    "t_stat = (treatment_mean - control_mean) / se\n",
    "df_degrees = n1 + n2 - 2\n",
    "p_values = 2 * (1 - stats.t.cdf(np.abs(t_stat), df_degrees))\n",
    "\n",
    "df['t_statistic'] = t_stat\n",
    "df['p_value'] = p_values\n",
    "df['-log10(p_value)'] = -np.log10(p_values)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"差异表达分析:\")\n",
    "print(df[['Gene", "t_statistic", "p_value", "-log10(p_value"]])"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 4. 火山图"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))\n",
    "plt.scatter(df['Log2_Fold_Change'], df['-log10(p_value)'], alpha=0.6)\n",
    "plt.axhline(y=-np.log10(0.05), color='r', linestyle='--', label='p=0.05')\n",
    "plt.axvline(x=np.log2(1.5), color='r', linestyle='--', label='FC=1.5')\n",
    "plt.axvline(x=np.log2(0.67), color='r', linestyle='--', label='FC=0.67')\n",
    "plt.xlabel('Log2 Fold Change')\n",
    "plt.ylabel('-log10(p-value)')\n",
    "plt.title('火山图')\n",
    "plt.legend()\n",
    "plt.grid(True, alpha=0.3)\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 5. MA图"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "df['M'] = df['Log2_Fold_Change']\n",
    "df['A'] = 0.5 * np.log2(df['Control_Mean'] * df['Treatment_Mean'])\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))\n",
    "plt.scatter(df['A'], df['M'], alpha=0.6)\n",
    "plt.axhline(y=0, color='r', linestyle='--', label='M=0')\n",
    "plt.xlabel('A (平均表达量)')\n",
    "plt.ylabel('M (Log2 Fold Change)')\n",
    "plt.title('MA图')\n",
    "plt.legend()\n",
    "plt.grid(True, alpha=0.3)\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 6. 练习\n",
    "\n",
    "### 练习1\n",
    "识别上调基因（Fold Change > 1.5 且 p < 0.05）\n",
    "\n",
    "### 练习2\n",
    "识别下调基因（Fold Change < 0.67 且 p < 0.05）\n",
    "\n",
    "### 练习3\n",
    "创建一个热图显示所有基因的表达水平"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 在这里编写你的练习代码\n",
    "\n",
    "# 练习1: 识别上调基因\n",
    "upregulated = df[(df['Fold_Change'] > 1.5) & (df['p_value'] < 0.05)]\n",
    "print(\"上调基因:\")\n",
    "print(upregulated[['Gene", "Fold_Change", "p_value"]])\n",
    "\n",
    "# 练习2: 识别下调基因\n",
    "downregulated = df[(df['Fold_Change'] < 0.67) & (df['p_value'] < 0.05)]\n",
    "print(\"\\n下调基因:\")\n",
    "print(downregulated[['Gene", "Fold_Change", "p_value"]])\n",
    "\n",
    "# 练习3: 创建热图\n",
    "import seaborn as sns\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))\n",
    "heatmap_data = df[['Control_1", "Control_2", "Treatment_1", "Treatment_2"]]\n",
    "heatmap_data.index = df['Gene']\n",
    "sns.heatmap(heatmap_data, annot=True, cmap='coolwarm', center=12)\n",
    "plt.title('基因表达热图')\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 7. 思考题\n",
    "\n",
    "1. Fold Change和Log2 Fold Change有什么区别？\n",
    "2. 为什么在差异表达分析中要同时考虑Fold Change和p值？\n",
    "3. 火山图和MA图有什么不同？\n",
    "4. 在什么情况下应该使用MA图而不是火山图？"
   ]
  }
 ],
